    "title": "京东开放平台免费上门退换服务规则",
    "followRuleId": "1092039123323195392",
    "content": "<h1 style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 2; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第一章 概述</span></strong></span></h1>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第一条</span></strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\"> 为提高消费者的购物体验，为商家提供更加便捷高效地售后服务单管理工具，特制定本规则。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第二条&nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">本规则适用于入驻京东开放平台JD.COM的SOP商家及开通自主售后的FBP商家（</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">经营机票/酒店/充值缴费/服务等无实物类目或特殊类目的商家除外，</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">参见规则附录一</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">）。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 2; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第三条&nbsp;&ldquo;</span></strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">免费上门退换&rdquo;服务是指商家通过签约投保&ldquo;运费险（升级版）&rdquo;开通<strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">&ldquo;</span></strong>免费上门退换&rdquo;服务后，对于在前台展示&ldquo;免费上门退换&rdquo;标识的商品，消费者发起退换货请求时，保险公司对退换货产生的单程运费提供保险服务（大件商品展示&ldquo;大件运费险&rdquo;标识，大件商品参见规则附录二）。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 2; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">第四条</span></strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\"> 开通&ldquo;免费上门退换&rdquo;服务能够有效地解决退货过程中买卖双方就运费支出产生的纠纷，减少商家的售后成本，提高消费者的售后体验，除经营机票/酒店/充值缴费/服务等无实物类目或特殊类目商品及自然人店铺的商家外，其他SOP商家及开通自主售后的FBP商家均应开通&ldquo;免费上门退换&rdquo;服务。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 2; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第五条 服务标识展示</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 2; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">（一）免费上门退换标识</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 2; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><img class=\"wscnph\" src=\"//img30.360buyimg.com/venderrule//jfs/t1/236273/21/14602/88131/66173f11Ff88fabc5/d0d93ecf83426dab.png\" width=\"300\" /></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 2; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">（二）大件运费险标识</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 2; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><img class=\"wscnph\" src=\"//img30.360buyimg.com/venderrule//jfs/t1/193300/39/42879/81825/66173ef8F263ff59a/698778e812c6aaa4.jpg\" width=\"300\" /></p>\n<h1 style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 2; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第二章 服务开通与退出</span></strong></span></h1>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 2; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第六条&nbsp;服务开通方式</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 2; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-weight: normal;\">（一）</span></strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">已签约运费险的商家需通过将运费险升级为 &ldquo;运费险（升级版）&rdquo;</span><strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\"> </span></strong><strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; font-weight: normal;\">加入&ldquo;免费上门退换&rdquo;服务</span></strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 2; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; font-weight: normal;\">（二）未签约运费险的商家需通过签约&ldquo;运费险（升级版）&rdquo;加入&ldquo;免费上门退换&rdquo;服务。</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 2; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; font-weight: normal;\">（三）商家参加</span></strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">平台级大促或秒杀、超级补贴等活动时，依据京东平台活动规则，商家均需通过签约&ldquo;运费险（升级版）&rdquo;的方式加入&ldquo;免费上门退换&rdquo;服务，启用时间段及适用类目等信息请参考相关规则，活动结束后商家可自行解约&ldquo;<span style=\"background: white;\">运费险（升级版）</span>&rdquo;，退出&ldquo;免费上门退换&rdquo;服务。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 2; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">（四）系统路径：商家后台-服务-保险服务-运费险（升级版）（申请开通后实时生效）。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 2; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第七条 服务退出方式</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 20pt; line-height: 200%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">商家可通过<span style=\"color: #2100ff;\">(<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><a style=\"color: #2100ff; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"http://3.cn/10eMb-gwI\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">http://3.cn/10eMb-gwI</a></span>)</span> 联系京东保险经纪在线客服解约（解约生效以前台实际下标时间为准）。</span></p>\n<h1 style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 2; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第三章 服务细则</span></strong></span></h1>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 2; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第八条</span></strong><strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\"> 投保规则</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-indent: 20pt; line-height: 2; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">商家作为投保人，为在京东平台上购买其所售商品的买家投保运费险（升级版），并向保险公司支付保险费。商家须为其退货包运费险投保期间所售的每一笔订单投保。买家以购物车形式拍下的每笔订单，将作为一个整体投保一次，如买家所购实际发货的订单不在大件物品投保适用品类中，但订单累计重量（订单累计重量=每件商品毛重*购买件数）大于20kg，则按照大件物品投保。如遇订单拆分情况，按照拆单后的子订单重量、类目规则执行，详情可查看具体协议。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 2; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第九条 理赔规则</span></strong></span></p>\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" style=\"width: 474.65pt; border-collapse: collapse; line-height: 2;\" border=\"0\" width=\"633\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 14.0pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 99.0pt; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.0pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"132\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">前台展示标识</span></strong></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 77.95pt; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-left: none; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.0pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"104\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">返件方式</span></strong></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 163.0pt; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-left: none; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.0pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"217\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">理赔规则</span></strong></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 134.7pt; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-left: none; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.0pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"180\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">理赔次数</span></strong></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 28.0pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 99.0pt; border-top: none; border-left: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 28.0pt;\" rowspan=\"2\" width=\"132\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">免费上门退换</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 77.95pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 28.0pt;\" width=\"104\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">上门取件</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 163.0pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 28.0pt;\" width=\"217\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">基础运费+包装费用。</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 134.7pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 28.0pt;\" rowspan=\"4\" width=\"180\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">每个订单中的每个商品支持一次理赔</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 84.0pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 77.95pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 84.0pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"104\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">用户自寄</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 163.0pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 84.0pt;\" width=\"217\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">按照目前市场所有物流公司中，相同路线最低首重价格赔付，续重价格保险公司不予赔付，实际理赔金额以最终到账为准，每次最高赔付金额为200元。</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 14.0pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 99.0pt; border-top: none; border-left: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.0pt;\" rowspan=\"2\" width=\"132\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">大件运费险</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 77.95pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.0pt;\" width=\"104\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">上门取件</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 163.0pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.0pt;\" width=\"217\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">基础运费+包装费用，最高赔付金额为800元。<br /></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 14.0pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 77.95pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.0pt;\" width=\"104\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">用户自寄</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 163.0pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.0pt;\" width=\"217\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">按照目前市场所有物流公司中，相同路线最低首重价格赔付，续重价格保险公司不予赔付，实际理赔金额以最终到账为准，每次最高赔付金额为200元。</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 2; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">第十条 权益规则</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 2; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">（一）商家开通&ldquo;免费上门退换&rdquo;服务后，将在PC /APP端等商详页打标&ldquo;免费上门退换&rdquo;标识，增加商品辨识度，有助于提高商家信誉和潜在转化率。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 2; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">（二）<span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">&ldquo;免费上门退换&rdquo;服务是店铺综合体验分售后服务加分项，有助于提升商家店铺综合体验分排名，从而获得相应流量及权益资源，详情可查看<u><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #2100ff; background: white;\"><a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1147722726895652864&amp;type=0&amp;btype=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"color: #2100ff;\">《京东开放平台店铺星级规则》</span></a></span></u><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #2100ff; background: white;\">。</span> </span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 2; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">（三）&ldquo;免费上门退换&rdquo;服务加入搜索排序因子，开通&ldquo;免费上门退换&rdquo;服务可提升搜索排序结果。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 2; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">第十一条</span></strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\"> 售后服务因子/交易纠纷因子得分排名低于60%的商家</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">需通过投保&ldquo;运费险（升级版）&rdquo;的方式加入&ldquo;免费上门退换&rdquo;<span style=\"background: white;\">服务，详情可查看<span style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: #2100ff;\"><a style=\"color: #2100ff; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=941277149179023360&amp;type=0&amp;btype=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">《<span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: white;\">京东开放平台商家服务管理规则》</span></a></span></span></span><span style=\"color: #2100ff;\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: white;\">。</span></span></span></p>\n<h1 style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 2; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第四章 附则</span></strong></span></h1>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 2; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第十二条&nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">京东开放平台商家的行为，发生在本管理规则生效之日以前的，适用当时的规则。发生在本管理规则生效之日以后的，适用本规则。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 2; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第十三条</span></strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\"> 平台可根据商家特征，为免费上门退换服务适配商家开通该服务。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 2; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第十四条&nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">京东可根据平台运营情况随时调整本管理规则并以&ldquo;京东开放平台&rdquo;公告的形式向商家公示；商家入驻京东即表示接受京东其后不时调整、颁布的管理规则。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 2; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第十五条&nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">商家应遵守国家法律、行政法规、部门规章等规范性文件。对任何涉嫌违反国家法律、行政法规、部门规章等规范性文件的行为，本规则已有规定的，适用于本规则。本规则尚无规定的，京东有权酌情处理。但京东对商家的处理不免除其应承担的法律责任。商家在京东的任何行为，应同时遵守与京东及其关联公司签订的各项协议；如有违约即视为对本规则的违反。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 2; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第十六条&nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">本规则于2024年4月11日发布，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">于2024年10月10日修订，于2024年10月17日生效。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 2; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">【附录】不支持运费险类目及<span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">大件物品投保适用品类信息请参考：<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: #2100ff; text-decoration: underline;\"><a style=\"color: #2100ff; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/hot-topic/detail?issueId=47165.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">《免费上门退换类目明细》</a></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>",
